Amazon Delivery Performance EDA

- Bussiness Problem
    Delivery performance can be affected by factors such as distance, traffic,
    weather, type of vehicle, and the delivery dirver. Logistics teams need to
    understand which factors have the greater impact of delivery efficiency to 
    provide top quality service.

- Analysis Goal
    Implement an EDA to :
        Quantify overall delivery time efficiency
        Identify key factors that impact delivery time
        Find segments with constant high or low delivery times
        Produce actionable recommendations 

- Dataset
    Amazon Delivey Dataset from Kaggle

- Tools Used
    Python
    Pandas
    Numpy
    Matplolib